A cyberpunk cityscape at dusk where towering skyscrapers are constructed entirely from interlocking puzzle pieces and geometric building blocks, each piece fitting perfectly into the next with mechanical precision. The buildings glow with neon circuitry patterns running through their surfaces like veins. In the foreground, identical rows of small humanoid figures move along illuminated pathways that branch in predetermined patterns like a circuit board. The sky is a gradient of deep purple and electric orange, with holographic grids overlaying the clouds. The entire scene suggests a metropolis designed on a blueprint, every element calculated and positioned with architectural exactness, yet beautiful in its rigid harmony.
